    very delicate and light, in a way that does not seem real
        缥缈的；超凡的；优雅的
            ethereal beauty 超凡的美丽
            His music is ethereal. 他的音乐超凡脱俗。

tortuous
    〔路、溪流等〕弯弯曲曲的，曲折的
    ★ 转弯抹角的，绕圈子的；复杂的；令人费解的
        complicated and long and therefore confusing

protracted
    长时间的；旷日持久的
        SYN lengthy
            protracted negotiations/discussions/debate etc

untether
    从系绳(或系链)上解下；放开
    untethered from

narcissistic  # /,nɑrsɪ'sɪstɪk/
