    牵强的；不可信的；靠不住的

unconscionable  # /ʌn'kɑnʃənəbl/  # conscious conscience
    much more than is reasonable or acceptable
        不合理的；过度的；难以接受的

conscionable
    凭良心的
        acceptable to one's conscience

