        in writing, a play etc, a sudden change from a subject that is beautiful, moral, or serious to something that is ordinary, silly, or not important
            突降法〔指作品内容突然由美好、严肃变成平庸可笑〕

bedeck  # /bɪ'dɛk/  # = deck out
